      "author": "LiveAQuietLife",
      "description": "## [1.0.4] - 2026-07-09\r\n\r\n### Fixed\r\n- Finish dates in the past are now blocked when activating a planned book or adding a book in \"start reading now\" mode, matching the rule Edit Schedule already enforced. Previously, a past finish date would compress the entire book into a single chunk due today with no warning.\r\n- The Start Reading modal now shows inline validation messages below the finish date field, same as Edit Schedule.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n- Due dates on planned books are intentionally unrestricted — a past due date on a book you haven't started is metadata, not a schedule commitment.",
